{"title":"EUROBIKE Announces Move to Frankfurt, earlier show dates & Fresh Concepts","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/06/eurobike-frankfurt-move/","date":1625600329000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>For years now, EUROBIKE has called the small German town of Friedrichshafen home. That all changes for 2022. Next year, the annual cycling showcase known as EUROBIKE will move from its long standing home outside of Lake Constance, to Frankfurt, Germany. Stamped across the event giant’s website is the statement, “We are changing the concept of EUROBIKE – both in terms of its content and staging.”</p><p>Let’s break that down.</p><figure id=\"attachment_264194\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-264194\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06153038/Eurobike-2022-moved-to-Frankfurt-images-from-Friedrichshafen.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06153038/Eurobike-2022-moved-to-Frankfurt-images-from-Friedrichshafen.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x363/rscb20/ng:webp/ngcb20\" alt=\"Friedrichshafen Germany replaced by Frankfurt for Eurobike 2022\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06153038/Eurobike-2022-moved-to-Frankfurt-images-from-Friedrichshafen.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb20 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06153038/Eurobike-2022-moved-to-Frankfurt-images-from-Friedrichshafen-297x223.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb20 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06153038/Eurobike-2022-moved-to-Frankfurt-images-from-Friedrichshafen-800x600.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb20 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06153038/Eurobike-2022-moved-to-Fra